videos.description: Blair Schaefer buries a deep 3-pointer for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Schaefer shows huge range with three

videos.description: Morgan Williams cuts through the Oregon defense and banks in a layup for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Williams cuts through defense and scores bank layup

videos.description: Chloe Bibby drives and dishes to Teaira McCowan for an easy layup and-1 for Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Bibby, McCowan combine for bucket and-1

videos.description: Victoria Vivians scores on the fast break to cap a 13-2 run for Mississippi State.

videos.description: Morgan Williams gets into the lane and scores a right-handed layup while drawing a foul for Mississippi State
videos.headline: Williams motors to the bucket for and-1

videos.description: Teaira McCowan blocks Oregon's Maite Cazorla's shot attempt in transition for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: McCowan's shot blocked in transition

videos.description: Teaira McCowan drains a bucket plus the foul off a pass from Victoria Vivians to extend the lead.
videos.headline: McCowan muscles in for layup and-1

videos.description: Victoria Vivians hits a 3-pointer from the right corner to extend the lead for the Bulldogs.
videos.headline: Vivians swishes corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Center Teaira McCowan records a career-high 35 points, 19 rebounds and five blocks as the Bulldogs win a marquee matchup against the Ducks.
videos.headline: No. 5 MSU makes statement in 90-79 win vs. No. 9 Oregon
